Petaluma Site Shutdown: Saturday, March 28 (5:00 AM–12:00 PM PT)
 
Due to power maintenance at the Petaluma site, IT will shut down systems on Saturday, March 28 from 5:00 AM–12:00 PM PT. During this time, VMs and lab systems will be unavailable for all Calix employees and contractors.
 
What to Know

·         Outage window: 5:00 AM–12:00 PM PT (3/28)
·         Impact: Petaluma VMs and lab environments offline
·         No action needed after—systems will be brought back online once power is restored.
